          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实指望扫东吴踏平江南。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "还有那诸葛亮诡计多端。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "蒋子翼引庞统来献连环。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又谁知诸葛亮力能回天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只剩下十八骑好不惨然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "正行间勒战马——"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "用目观看，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在中原领人马八十三万"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又谁知小周郎谋略广远"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄公覆他把那苦肉计献"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我只说数九天东风少见"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "烧得我众兵将头焦肉烂"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "丞相发笑为哪般？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "笑只笑周郎见识浅，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孔明袖内少机关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只恐性命难保全。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖内喊声〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一言未尽人呐喊，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "旌旗招展心胆寒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "许褚，看看是什么人的旗号？"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（许褚看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是“关”字旗号。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我谢天谢地。"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "事到如今，还谢的什么天地？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那关云长曾许我三不死，难道今日一死也不饶么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等杀不得了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用你们杀了。就在此地歇息歇息。"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、张辽、许褚、曹洪同席地坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听说来了关美髯，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由孟德喜心间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "问声君侯驾可安？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹操打躬。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关平、周仓",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操到！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关羽 （内西皮导板） 耳旁厢又听得人嘶马闹，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽上。关平、周仓、关羽同上高台，同亮相。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "展蚕眉睁凤眼仔细观瞧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯，别来无恙啊？哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "狭路上莫不是冤家来到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "故友相逢，怎说冤家二字？言重了哇！哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奉军令谁认你旧日故交！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹孟德在马上满脸赔笑，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尊一声二君侯细听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "望君侯开大恩放我回朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在赤壁中火攻败兵来到"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三国中论奸雄算你曹操，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一派的假殷勤袖内藏刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "俺今日用兵时何必发笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奉军令捉拿你怎肯相饶！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我中了小周郎苦肉计巧，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只烧得众兵丁皮开肉焦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二君侯若不信仔细观瞧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只剩下十八骑败兵来到"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周将！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "查看曹操还有多少人马？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周仓下高台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们站起来！一五，一十，一、二、三。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一十八骑残兵败将。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周仓上高台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军师呀，军师！你既能算，却不能料。慢说一十八骑残兵败将，就是一十八只"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猛虎，何足道哉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我看他好一似鳌鱼吞钓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "惊弓鸟插双翅也难飞逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说什么我好似鳌鱼吞钓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说什么惊弓鸟也难飞逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上马金下马银美酒红袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你本是大义人怎忘故交？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想当初待君侯恩高义好"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "官封你汉寿亭侯爵禄不少"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你虽然待我的恩高义好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我也曾答报了汗马功劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将印信悬高梁封金辞曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "斩颜良诛文丑立功报效"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我也曾命张辽文凭送到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "临行时我又送美酒红袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "休提起送文凭令人可恼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "诛孔秀，刺孟、韩，王植被枭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谢丞相假人情哪在心梢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "过黄河斩秦琪文凭才到"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在许昌曾许我云阳答报，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你本是大义人岂忘故交！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "非是我忘却了云阳答报，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "皆因你这奸曹罪恶难饶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "挟天子令诸侯势压群僚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "害董承斩马腾欲谋汉朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恨不得拿住你剥皮楦草。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上前来试一试偃月钢刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在许田射鹿时把君欺藐"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "逼死了董贵妃其罪非小"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹孟德在马上苦苦哀告，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君侯哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你何不留美名在那万古标。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "往日杀人不眨眼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "铁打心肠软如棉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "左思右想难上难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "宁斩我头挂高杆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "释放曹操回中原。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "背地只把军师怨"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "关某岂做无义汉"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "摆开一字长蛇阵"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "许褚，看看什么阵势？"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（许褚看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃一字长蛇阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想是关羽有意放你我逃走。走了罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好个仁义关美髯，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "释放曹操回中原。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "再领人马报仇冤。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹操、四龙套、张辽、许褚、曹洪同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周仓",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操逃走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回营交令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关平、周仓、关羽同下高台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "悔当初错许他云阳答报，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到今日顺人情又犯律条。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "就说是关二爷释放奸曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一腔热血染战袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽上马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "汗马功劳一旦抛！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
